361
00:20:51.716 --> 00:20:54.926
NEAT1, but more specifically, he could see that

362
00:20:54.976 --> 00:20:58.376
the long isoform, the paraspeckle

363
00:20:58.456 --> 00:21:01.516
isoform, increased significantly,

364
00:21:02.216 --> 00:21:06.196
and there were more NEAT1 foci per nucleus

365
00:21:06.256 --> 00:21:07.096
in those cells.

366
00:21:09.336 --> 00:21:09.576
So

367
00:21:10.476 --> 00:21:13.696
next, Dikari asked, "How do these cells respond to the

368
00:21:13.756 --> 00:21:17.216
