369
00:21:17.856 --> 00:21:21.796
these Sut2 cells which have NEAT1 knocked

370
00:21:21.896 --> 00:21:22.266
down,

371
00:21:23.676 --> 00:21:26.936
as we saw before, there's an increase in the sensitivity.

372
00:21:28.116 --> 00:21:32.096
But if you instead knock out quaking, so you increase the

373
00:21:32.496 --> 00:21:35.076
