376
00:21:43.696 --> 00:21:44.956
cells.

377
00:21:46.076 --> 00:21:48.366
And so these experiments

378
00:21:50.576 --> 00:21:54.276
place quaking upstream of

379
00:21:54.336 --> 00:21:57.836
NEAT1 in the biogenesis of paraspeckles.

380
00:21:58.596 --> 00:22:01.846
And so this is really a dynamic process.

381
00:22:02.536 --> 00:22:06.026
So, not only is this cell type dependent,

382
00:22:07.096 --> 00:22:11.016
but these factors are responsive to stress.

383
00:22:11.096 --> 00:22:14.556
For example, NEAT1 can be upregulated

384
00:22:14.956 --> 00:22:16.116
