482
00:28:00.656 --> 00:28:04.276
So you can imagine that having this ready pool upon

483
00:28:04.816 --> 00:28:08.696
a signal to be spliced is important

484
00:28:08.756 --> 00:28:11.996
there. In other cases, though, these actually

485
00:28:12.076 --> 00:28:14.576
