1273
01:14:30.752 --> 01:14:34.672
at UCI in computational biology, Beatrice Zhang, in our group, and was

1274
01:14:34.712 --> 01:14:38.672
a collaboration with the other folks you see listed here, including really talented

1275
01:14:38.732 --> 01:14:42.472
surgeon scientists at MSK, Sharl Ailian, and T cell

1276
01:14:42.532 --> 01:14:44.812
biologists Chris Klebanoff and Santosh Verdanna.

1277
01:14:45.292 --> 01:14:47.612
