1286
01:15:24.332 --> 01:15:28.272
program of exhausted T cells. So basically, in short, we think that

1287
01:15:28.312 --> 01:15:32.232
there's an accessory splicing factor that's upregulated on the T cell state

1288
01:15:32.272 --> 01:15:35.512
that regulates that splicing event, is the general idea of what we think is

1289
01:15:35.592 --> 01:15:36.012
happening.

1290
01:15:36.472 --> 01:15:37.592
Mm-hmm. Okay. Thank you.

